channel.title: Delta Doors
channel.description: Hey guys. I know you probably think that im asking how to use doors, but im not. I know how. the problem im having is doors will not open no matter what. ive tested to confirm this (copy and pasted the doors.cfg to multiple sources) and it works on all of them except this one. [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=532694.0]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=532694.0[/url] I was wondering if maybe, since it's cleaned, he might've locked or commented a door code? if anyone can help me i would greatly appreciate it. also if you need any additional info please ask and ill get it right away.
